uggest that they do.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On the other hand it is inconvenient and disru=
ptive that Microsoft had to effectively veto Altman=E2=80=99s firing after =
it happened? Better to be told first and head it off. Thus, board observer.=
</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Here=E2=80=99s <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bl=
oombergbusiness.com/click/33537957.286427/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS90ZWNoL=
