-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; back=
ground-color: #ccc;"> one other piece of news</a>, sort of, about the new b=
oard chair, Bret Taylor, =E2=80=9Cthe former co-CEO of business-software gi=
ant Salesforce who also was the chairman of Twitter when it dealt with Elon=
 Musk=E2=80=99s ultimately successful takeover effort=E2=80=9D:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">OpenAI=E2=80=99s board is unusual in that it i=
sn=E2=80=99t obligated to maximize shareholder value, but rather to fulfill=
 a larger mission of advancing artificial intelligence for humanity=E2=80=
=99s benefit. On its website, OpenAI says the board=E2=80=99s =E2=80=9Cprin=
cipal beneficiary is humanity, not OpenAI investors.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Asked if OpenAI=E2=80=99s board could revisit =
this structure, Taylor said: =E2=80=9CI think it=E2=80=99s a great question=
=E2=80=94probably not one for my first day on the job.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That=E2=80=99s one possible answer! I mean, I =
guess technically it=E2=80=99s a non-answer, but it=E2=80=99s an interestin=
g one.=C2=A0=E2=80=9CShould you benefit humanity or your investors?=E2=80=
=9D =E2=80=9CGreat question, not sure yet.=E2=80=9D There are other possibl=
e answers! =E2=80=9CNo, the nonprofit structure is at the core of what we d=
o, this company is fundamentally about benefiting humanity, that=E2=80=99s =
what the investors and employees signed up for,=C2=A0and that part is reall=
y nonnegotiable=E2=80=9D is, for instance, an imaginable answer. You could =
imagine the old nonprofit board, as a condition of letting Altman back, dem=
anding =E2=80=9Clook you can bring in new, more commercial directors, but t=
he nonprofit structure has to stay.=E2=80=9D But they ... didn=E2=80=99t do=
 that? Apparently? And Taylor is, like, for-profit-curious?</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Incidentally, when Taylor and the Twitter Inc.=
 board agreed to sell to Musk, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusine=
ss.com/click/33537957.286427/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2=
FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDUtMDIvdHdpdHRlci1zLWJvYXJkLWdhdmUtdXA_Y21waWQ9QkJEMTEzM=
DIzX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRt=
